'''飞行航线'''，也称为'''航路'''、'''空中走廊'''（{{lang-en|Airway}}）指的是飞机在机场间行进时应该遵守的[[航线|航线]]。<ref>{{cite book|last=Gunston|first=Bill|title=The Cambridge Aerospace Dictionary Cambridge|url=https://archive.org/details/cambridgeaerospa00guns|url-access=limited|publisher=Cambridge University Press|year=2004|isbn=978-0521841405|pages=[https://archive.org/details/cambridgeaerospa00guns/page/n43 34]}}</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20120309151642/http://www.faa.gov/air_traffic/publications/atpubs/aim/aim0503.html FAA regulations 5-3-4. Airways and Route Systems] in Section 3. En Route Procedures; archived from ''www.faa.gov'', accessed 25 October 2020</ref><ref>[http://www.skybrary.aero/index.php/Airway Airway (definition)- Airway Description] ''www.skybrary.aero'', accessed 25 October 2020</ref>飞行航线是由一个个带有高度区间和宽度的的直线段组成。这些直线段可以是[[卫星导航系统|卫星导航系统]]提供的坐标点，也可以是由地基{{tsl|en|navigational aid|助航裝置}}[[发送器|发送器]]（如[[甚高频全向信标|VOR]]、[[歸航台|NDB]]）及多个信号台产生的{{tsl|en|Intersection (aviation)|交点 (飞行)|航向交点}}组成。

